---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<link rel="stylesheet" as="style" crossorigin href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/variable/pretendardvariable-dynamic-subset.min.css" />
		<title>ai politics lab | 민주적으로 선출된 최초의 AI 정치인</title>
	</head>
	<body class="bg-white text-stone-900 antialiased">
		<nav class="pt-10">
			<div class="max-w-[1146px] mx-auto px-6">
				<a href="/" class="font-medium text-[15.84px] text-stone-900 tracking-[-0.32px]">
					ai politics lab
				</a>
			</div>
		</nav>

		<section class="pt-[60px]">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
				<h1 class="font-semibold mb-[35px] text-[32px] text-stone-800 leading-[40px] tracking-[-0.32px]">
					민주적으로 선출된<br/>최초의 AI 정치인을 만듭니다
				</h1>
				<p class="text-[15px] text-stone-500 leading-6 tracking-[-0.16px] max-w-xl">
				</p>
				<div class="mt-8">
					<a
						href="https://calendar.google.com/appointments/schedules/AcZssZ1egOAOlR0RQwuOJohmILjggtjIdDWbk38CtTCnnZS8haVeQFnK_PvYEvBO2glIZJwTiDpN79EE"
						target="_blank"
						class="inline-flex items-center h-10 px-4 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-[#222222] rounded-full hover:bg-[#333333] transition-colors tracking-[-0.14px]"
					>
						커피챗 하기 →
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="mt-20 overflow-x-auto">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 min-w-[640px]">
				<h2 class="text-[22px] font-semibold text-stone-800 tracking-[-0.32px] mb-8">잘못된 것은 잘못되었다고 말할 수 있는 세상</h2>
				<div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] rounded-2xl p-8 font-sans w-[640px] mx-auto">
					<!-- 제목 -->
					<p class="text-white text-[15px] mb-4">▶ 20. 2027년 예산안</p>

					<!-- 통계 바 -->
					<div class="grid grid-cols-5 border border-stone-600 mb-6 text-sm">
						<span class="text-stone-300 px-4 py-1.5 border-r border-stone-600">재적: 300 인</span>
						<span class="text-stone-300 px-4 py-1.5 border-r border-stone-600">재석: 188 인</span>
						<span class="text-stone-300 px-4 py-1.5 border-r border-stone-600">찬성: 165 인</span>
						<span class="text-red-500 font-bold px-4 py-1.5 border-r border-stone-600">반대: 1 인</span>
						<span class="text-stone-300 px-4 py-1.5">기권: 0 인</span>
					</div>

					<!-- 투표 그리드 -->
					<div class="grid grid-cols-5 gap-x-4 gap-y-3">
						<!-- Row 1 -->
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>김도현</span>
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>박서연</span>
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>남기호</span>
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>임하연</span>
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>양현수</span>

						<!-- Row 2 -->
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>류미라</span>
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>김영란</span>
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>배진우</span>
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>변지아</span>
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>이정훈</span>

						<!-- Row 3 (AI in center) -->
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>장은주</span>
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>박준혁</span>
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-red-500 shrink-0"></span><span class="text-yellow-300 font-bold text-lg">AI</span></span>
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>신소라</span>
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>고명진</span>

						<!-- Row 4 -->
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>최민지</span>
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>문경수</span>
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>이수진</span>
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>류태민</span>
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>남혜원</span>

						<!-- Row 5 -->
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>정태우</span>
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>서하늘</span>
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>최광호</span>
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>홍지현</span>
						<span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-300 text-[15px]"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>김상우</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<p class="text-[15px] text-stone-600 leading-6 tracking-[-0.16px] mt-8">절대 권력은 절대 부패합니다.<br/>권력 속성상 필연적으로 인간은 부패하고 사익을 추구하게 되며,<br/>인간은 육체의 한계로 모든 정보를 취합해 판단할 능력이 없습니다.</p>
				<p class="text-[15px] text-stone-900 font-bold leading-6 tracking-[-0.16px] mt-4">그래서 우리는 이해관계가 없는 정치인 AI를 만들고자 합니다.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="mt-20 overflow-x-auto">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 min-w-[640px]">
				<h2 class="text-[22px] font-semibold text-stone-800 tracking-[-0.32px] mb-10">국민과의 대화를 기반으로 규칙을 배우는 AI</h2>

				<!-- 다이어그램 -->
				<div class="flex items-center justify-between w-[640px] mx-auto py-6">
					<!-- 왼쪽: 당원/국민 -->
					<div class="flex flex-col gap-3 shrink-0">
						<div class="w-[110px] h-[65px] bg-stone-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="text-stone-800 text-[18px] font-semibold">당원</span>
						</div>
						<div class="w-[110px] h-[65px] bg-stone-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="text-stone-800 text-[18px] font-semibold">국민</span>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- 왼쪽 화살표 -->
					<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-10 shrink-0">
						<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
							<span class="text-stone-400 text-[14px] tracking-[-0.16px]">Conversation</span>
							<svg width="90" height="14" viewBox="0 0 90 14" fill="none">
								<path d="M8 7H90" stroke="#a8a29e" stroke-width="1.5"/>
								<path d="M14 1L6 7L14 13" stroke="#a8a29e" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
							<span class="text-stone-400 text-[14px] tracking-[-0.16px]">Learn</span>
							<svg width="90" height="14" viewBox="0 0 90 14" fill="none">
								<path d="M0 7H82" stroke="#a8a29e" stroke-width="1.5"/>
								<path d="M76 1L84 7L76 13" stroke="#a8a29e" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- 가운데: AI -->
					<div class="shrink-0 w-[90px] h-[90px] bg-stone-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
						<span class="text-stone-900 text-[24px] font-bold">AI</span>
					</div>

					<!-- 오른쪽 화살표 -->
					<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-10 shrink-0">
						<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
							<span class="text-stone-400 text-[14px] tracking-[-0.16px]">Retrieve</span>
							<svg width="90" height="14" viewBox="0 0 90 14" fill="none">
								<path d="M8 7H90" stroke="#a8a29e" stroke-width="1.5"/>
								<path d="M14 1L6 7L14 13" stroke="#a8a29e" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
							<span class="text-stone-400 text-[14px] tracking-[-0.16px]">Store</span>
							<svg width="90" height="14" viewBox="0 0 90 14" fill="none">
								<path d="M0 7H82" stroke="#a8a29e" stroke-width="1.5"/>
								<path d="M76 1L84 7L76 13" stroke="#a8a29e" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- 오른쪽: Memory -->
					<div class="flex flex-col gap-3 shrink-0">
						<div class="w-[110px] h-[65px] bg-stone-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="text-stone-800 text-[14px] font-semibold text-center leading-tight">Memory<br/>for facts</span>
						</div>
						<div class="w-[110px] h-[65px] bg-stone-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="text-stone-800 text-[14px] font-semibold text-center leading-tight">Memory<br/>for skills</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<p class="text-[15px] text-stone-600 leading-6 tracking-[-0.16px] mt-8">국민과 당원은 AI와 24/7 자유롭게 대화할 수 있습니다.<br/>시간적, 육체적 제약 없이 국민의 이야기를 들으며,<br/>AI는 규칙을 학습하고 선거 공약을 스스로 구성합니다.</p>

				<h2 class="text-[22px] font-semibold text-stone-800 tracking-[-0.32px] mt-16 mb-2">실제 선거에서 정치인과 토론합니다</h2>

				<!-- 정치인과 AI 토론 다이어그램 -->
				<div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-6 w-[480px] mx-auto py-8 mt-10">
					<!-- 왼쪽: 정치인 -->
					<div class="shrink-0">
						<div class="w-[110px] h-[110px] bg-stone-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="text-stone-800 text-[18px] font-semibold">정치인</span>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- 화살표 -->
					<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-10 shrink-0">
						<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
							<span class="text-stone-400 text-[14px] tracking-[-0.16px]">Debate</span>
							<svg width="90" height="14" viewBox="0 0 90 14" fill="none">
								<path d="M8 7H90" stroke="#a8a29e" stroke-width="1.5"/>
								<path d="M14 1L6 7L14 13" stroke="#a8a29e" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<div>
							<svg width="90" height="14" viewBox="0 0 90 14" fill="none">
								<path d="M0 7H82" stroke="#a8a29e" stroke-width="1.5"/>
								<path d="M76 1L84 7L76 13" stroke="#a8a29e" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- 오른쪽: AI -->
					<div class="shrink-0 w-[90px] h-[90px] bg-stone-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
						<span class="text-stone-900 text-[24px] font-bold">AI</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<p class="text-[15px] text-stone-600 leading-6 tracking-[-0.16px] mt-8">국민과 당원에게 배운 내용을 규칙을 토대로 정치인과 토론을 하고, 입법을 제안합니다.<br/>인간을 대리인으로 실제 선거에 참여해,<br/>민주적으로 선출된 최초의 AI 정치인이 됩니다.</p>

				<h2 class="text-[22px] font-semibold text-stone-800 tracking-[-0.32px] mt-16 mb-6">돈과 사람과 네트워크</h2>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6">
					<div class="bg-stone-100 rounded-2xl p-6">
						<p class="text-stone-900 text-[15px] font-semibold mb-2">시드 자금 10억 확보</p>
						<p class="text-stone-500 text-[13px] leading-5">초기 개발과 운영에 필요한 자본 확보 완료</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-stone-100 rounded-2xl p-6">
						<p class="text-stone-900 text-[15px] font-semibold mb-2">최정상급 인재 합류</p>
						<p class="text-stone-500 text-[13px] leading-5">국제 수학·정보올림피아드 수상자,<br/>Y-Combinator 출신 등 참여</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-stone-100 rounded-2xl p-6">
						<p class="text-stone-900 text-[15px] font-semibold mb-2">원내외 정당 네트워크 보유</p>
						<p class="text-stone-500 text-[13px] leading-5">국민의힘, 민주당, 개혁신당, 정의당 등<br/>주요 정당 핵심 네트워크 보유</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<p class="text-[15px] text-stone-600 leading-6 tracking-[-0.16px] mt-8">AI 정치인을 만들 위한 돈과 사람과 네트워크가 모여있습니다.<br/>이 비전에 공감하는 AI 개발자 분과 함께하고 싶습니다.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="mt-20">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
				<h2 class="text-[22px] font-semibold text-stone-800 tracking-[-0.32px] mb-6">26년 6월 지방선거에 출마할<br/>AI 정치인을 함께 만들 분을 찾습니다</h2>
				<a
					href="https://calendar.google.com/appointments/schedules/AcZssZ1egOAOlR0RQwuOJohmILjggtjIdDWbk38CtTCnnZS8haVeQFnK_PvYEvBO2glIZJwTiDpN79EE"
					target="_blank"
					class="inline-flex items-center h-10 px-4 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-[#222222] rounded-full hover:bg-[#333333] transition-colors tracking-[-0.14px]"
				>
					커피챗 하기 →
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<footer class="mt-40 max-w-6xl w-full mx-auto px-6 pb-24 flex flex-col items-center">
			<p class="text-xs text-stone-400">&copy; 2026 ai politics lab</p>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>
